<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509074' id='t-509074'>Now 110 countries are accessing it. Okay?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='513636' id='t-513636'>So I classify the people into three:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517636' id='t-517636'>uneducated, little educated, surplus educated.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524558' id='t-524558'>Little educated, done this. Surplus educated,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='528449' id='t-528449'>what are you going to do for the society?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529853' id='t-529853'>Thank you very much. Bye!</span>
